### 教师创建课程
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseName": "概率论与数理统计",
  "description": "面向软件2301班的概率论课程",
  "teacherId": 1
}

### 查看全部课程
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses/list

### 查看教师课程
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses/teacher/1

### 学生加入课程
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "studentId": 2
}

### 学生查看我的课程
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses/my/2